Natasha Melnick https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Natasha_Melnick 0 Natasha Melnick (born April 10, 1984) is an American television and film actress. She is perhaps best known for her role as Cindy Sanders on the short-lived 1999 NBC comedy-drama Freaks and Geeks.
